Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:58.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}不知何时 微风在身边刮起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}但我并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:07.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}我只能尽力去传达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:14.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}每当迷茫 困惑 受伤之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:18.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}双手之间满载的记忆
